	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				At level 8, Enchater's get a spell called &quot;Chaotic Feedback&quot;, which will do 43 points of damage initialy, plus 1 point for every level above 8. Quite a nice spell.  The benefits of their ability to become other races are wonderful as well.  Just think. Become a half-elf, gain infravision. Need to regenerate? Become a troll.  By far, this class can be the wildcard of a party, and add lots of fun.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
