				About pets and charm/beguile...<BR>
<BR>
Your pets that you summon cannot be controlled... Common knowledge...<BR>
<BR>
Pets you charm/beguile CAN be controlled just like any other classes pets...<BR>
So you get all the commands... /pet attack /pet stay and so forth...<BR>
But only with charmed pets...!
